## 🚀 Quick Start

### 5분 안에 시작하기
```bash
# 1. Clone
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/stochastic-code-optimizer.git
cd stochastic-code-optimizer

# 2. Build
mkdir build && cd build
cmake .. && cmake --build .

# 3. Run Example
./stochastic_optimizer \
  --input ../examples/loop_tiling.mlir \
  --max-iterations 100 \
  --verbose

# 4. View Results
cat optimization_result.json
```

**상세 가이드**: [GETTING_STARTED.md](GETTING_STARTED.md)

